# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo AND in the working tree on every
# platform. `eol=lf` overrides a contributor's `core.autocrlf=true` (the Windows
# default), which would otherwise check files out as CRLF. That matters because
# Biome is configured with `lineEnding: "lf"` (see biome.json), so a CRLF working
# tree makes `check:ci` fail on every file.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never treat as text or normalize line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.db binary
*.pdf binary
